results.name: Decimal expansion of the constant c such that A007018(n)=floor(c^(2^n)).
reference: N. Gast, B. Gaujal, Infinite labeled trees: from rational to Sturmian trees, Theor. Comput. Sci. 411 (2010) 1146-1166, Section 5.2.
formula: c = E^2 where E is the Vardi constant arising in the Sylvester sequence (A076393). - _Gerald McGarvey_, Dec 08 2007
